<authorityName pageId="null" pageNumber="638">L.</authorityName>
gallicum
</italic>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2)
</td>
</tr>
<tr pageId="null" pageNumber="638">
<td align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" valign="top">
2*. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
blau, lila, rosa oder 
<normalizedToken originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">weiss</normalizedToken>
, 9-35 mm lang; Frucht 3-8 mm lang.
</td>
</tr>
<tr pageId="null" pageNumber="638">
<td align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" valign="top">
3. Stengel zuunterst sehr kurz behaart; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
am Rande mit 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Drüsenhaaren" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Druesenhaaren</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
hellrosa bis lila
</td>
<td align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" valign="bottom">
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Linaceae" genus="Linum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tenuifolium">
<italic pageId="null" pageNumber="638">
<authorityName pageId="null" pageNumber="638">L.</authorityName>
tenuifolium
</italic>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 3)
</td>
</tr>
<tr pageId="null" pageNumber="638">
<td align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" valign="top">
3*. Stengel kahl; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
auch am Rande kahl; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
blau (oft sehr hell)
</td>
</tr>
<tr pageId="null" pageNumber="638">
<td align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" valign="top">
4. Narbe 
<normalizedToken originalValue="eiförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">eifoermig</normalizedToken>
(bedeutend 
<normalizedToken originalValue="kürzer" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">kuerzer</normalizedToken>
als 0,8 nun); Frucht oft etwas nach unten gebogen.
</td>
</tr>
<tr pageId="null" pageNumber="638">
<td align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" valign="top">
5. Frucht 6-8 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
hellblau; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
vor der 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Bluete</normalizedToken>
nach unten gebogen (Knospen 
<normalizedToken originalValue="hängend" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">haengend</normalizedToken>
); Pflanze 10-30 cm hoch
</td>
<td align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" valign="bottom">
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Linaceae" genus="Linum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpinum">
<italic pageId="null" pageNumber="638">
<authorityName pageId="null" pageNumber="638">L.</authorityName>
alpinum
</italic>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 4)
</td>
</tr>
<tr pageId="null" pageNumber="638">
<td align="left" pageId="null" pageNumber="638" valign="top">
5*. Frucht 4-6 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
leuchtend blau; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="638">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
